<mvc:View controllerName="cpro.ui5.__kunde__.__projekt__.controller.Home" displayBlock="true" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc">
    <Page navButtonPress="navToHome" showNavButton="true" title="{i18n>label-about}">
        <l:BlockLayout background="Dashboard" class="ui-center-container">
            <l:BlockLayoutRow accentCells="Accent1">
                <l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    <VBox alignItems="Center" width="24em">
                        <Image class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom" src="assets/cpro-logo.jpg" height="80px" />
                        <Title class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>app-title}" />
                    </VBox>

                    <VBox class="sapUiMediumMarginBottom" alignItems="Center" width="24em">
                        <Text class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>app-description}" />
                        <Link target="_blank" href="https://www.cpro-iot.de/" text="{i18n>about-href-cpro}" />
                    </VBox>
                    <Panel expandable="true" width="24em" headerText="{i18n>about-attributions}">
                        <content>
                            <Link href="https://docs.sheetjs.com/docs/miscellany/license" text="SheetJS is licensed under the Apache 2.0 License" />
                            <Link href="https://github.com/SAP/openui5/blob/master/LICENSE.txt" text="OpenUI5 is licensed under the Apache 2.0 License" />
                        </content>
                    </Panel>
                </l:BlockLayoutCell>
            </l:BlockLayoutRow>
        </l:BlockLayout>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>